# ─── Auto-injected by Upstash Vercel Marketplace Integration ─────────────────
# These are the only environment variables this app needs.
# When deploying via the one-click button, they are automatically provisioned
# and injected by the Upstash integration — no manual setup required.
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=https://your-redis-url.upstash.io
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=your-redis-token
#
# Note: There is no SESSION_SECRET variable. The admin session signing key is
# derived automatically from UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN, so zero extra config
# is needed beyond the two variables above.
